com.interpss.opf

Interface IncrementalCost

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IncrementalCostImpl

    public interface IncrementalCost
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Incremental Cost'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Cost Model
    • Piece Wise Curve
    • Quadratic Curve
    See Also:
    OpfPackage.getIncrementalCost()
